></div><div style="padding-bottom:56.1%" class="image-hydration-wrapper sc-1eow4w5-3 iJyiXs"><div><img src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==" alt="Illustration for article titled The 50 most important American independent movies" data-srcset="https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fill,f_auto,fl_progressive,g_center,h_80,q_80,w_80/wsdclfty0ipzdu3h0cae.png 80w, https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fit,fl_progressive,q_80,w_320/wsdclfty0ipzdu3h0cae.png 320w, https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fit,f_auto,fl_progressive,q_80,w_470/wsdclfty0ipzdu3h0cae.png 470w, https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,fl_progressive,q_80,w_800/wsdclfty0ipzdu3h0cae.png 800w" draggable="auto" data-chomp-id="wsdclfty0ipzdu3h0cae" data-format="png" data-alt="Illustration for article titled The 50 most important American independent movies" data-anim-src=""/></div></div></span><figcaption class="no-caption sc-7s1ndr-0 fbAnrV">Photo<!-- -->: <!-- -->Trailer screenshot</figcaption></div><span data-id="wsdclfty0ipzdu3h0cae" data-recommend-id="image://wsdclfty0ipzdu3h0cae" data-format="png" data-width="1178" data-height="661" data-lightbox="true" data-recommended="false" class="js_recommend"></span></figure><p class="sc-77igqf-0 hJpRRP">Andrew Bujalski’s debut feature is widely considered to be the starting point of “mumblecore,” which flooded American film festivals and arthouse theaters with chatty, semi-improvised, conflict-averse, dirt-cheap indies that mostly involved millennials navigating the prospects of early adulthood. Few of these movies seemed to have keyed in to the humanist instincts that Bujalski would develop in his subsequent films. But though mumblecore was always more of a catch-all trend than a concerted movement, its surprising longevity (and flexibility) helped bring forth an impressive and eclectic array of major talents, including Bujalski, Greta Gerwig, Barry Jenkins, Alex Ross Perry, and the Safdie brothers. [Ignatiy Vishnevetsky]<br/></p><div class="js_movable_ad_slot bxm4mm-7 bhZEGl"><div class="bxm4mm-9 jgnxje"><label class="bxm4mm-8 kLAkkQ">Advertisement</label><div is="bulbs-dfp" class="ad-container dfp dfp-slot-MID_BANNER ad-middleboard" data-ad-unit="MID_BANNER" data-targeting="{&quot;pos&quot;:&quot;mid_banner&quot;}"></div><div class="bt-wrapper"><span data-uid="5d1b8a6cd5-384" class="bt-uid-tg" style="display:none !important;text-align:center" data-css-selector="ad-container.ad-middleboard"></span></div></div></div><hr class="gcp5ez-1 dqsVuw"/><h2 class="sc-1bwb26k-1 RjwRf" id="h220637"><a class="js_header-anchor" id=""></a><span><a class="sc-145m8ut-0 jwQTmy js_link sc-1out364-0 fwjlmD" data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;Internal link&quot;,&quot;https://film.avclub.com/how-did-my-big-fat-greek-wedding-make-so-much-money-1842133129&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://film.avclub.com/how-did-my-big-fat-greek-wedding-make-so-much-money-1842133129"><em>My Big Fat Greek Wedding</em></a></span> (2002)</h2><p class="sc-77igqf-0 hJpRRP"><span><a class="sc-145m8ut-0 jwQTmy js_link sc-1out364-0 fwjlmD" data-ga="[[&quot;Commerce&quot;,&quot;avfilm - The 50 most important American independent movies&quot;,&quot;&quot;]]" href="https://www.amazon.com/gp/video/detail/amzn1.dv.gti.90a9f711-e151-41e0-a2ff-4e908fe54747?ascsubtag=25c37b1b715416666d984f14ed1c7634b1637015&amp;autoplay=1&amp;tag=kinjaavclub-20" target="_top" data-amazonasin="" data-amazontag="kinjaavclub-20" data-amazonsubtag="[t|link[p|1842597128[au|5876237249237148780[b|avclub[lt|text"><strong><em>Amazon Prime</em></strong></a></span><strong><em>, </em></strong><span><a class="sc-145m8ut-0 jwQTmy js_link sc-1out364-0 fwjlmD" data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;External link&quot;,&quot;https://play.google.com/store/movies/details?id=hE_XKBxnw2o&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://play.google.com/store/movies/details?id=hE_XKBxnw2o" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><strong><em>Google Play</em></strong></a></span><strong><em>, </em></strong><span><a class="sc-145m8ut-0 jwQTmy js_link sc-1out364-0 fwjlmD" data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;External link&quot;,&quot;https://itunes.apple.com/us/movie/my-big-fat-greek-wedding/id325572996&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://itunes.apple.com/us/movie/my-big-fat-greek-wedding/id325572996" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><strong><em>iTunes</em></strong></a></span><strong><em>, </em></strong><span><a class="sc-145m8ut-0 jwQTmy js_link sc-1out364-0 fwjlmD" data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;External link&quot;,&quot;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hE_XKBxnw2o&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hE_XKBxnw2o" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><strong><em>YouTube</em></strong></a></span><strong><em>, </em></strong><span><a class="sc-145m8ut-0 jwQTmy js_link sc-1out364-0 fwjlmD" data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;External link&quot;,&quot;https://www.vudu.com/content/movies/details/My-Big-Fat-Greek-Wedding/29830&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://www.vudu.com/content/movies/details/My-Big-Fat-Greek-Wedding/29830" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><strong><em>VUDU</em></strong></a></span><strong><em>, Hulu (with Cinemax)</em></strong></p><figure class="align--bleed js_lazy-image js_marquee-assetfigure sc-1eow4w5-1 kivedT" data-id="t8rssjviq8bojg6fwzs3" data-recommend-id="image://t8rssjviq8bojg6fwzs3" data-format="png" data-width="1352" data-height="761" data-lightbox="true" data-recommended="false" contenteditable="false" draggable="false"><div class="img-wrapper sc-1eow4w5-2 gfolHV" contenteditable="false" style="max-width:1352px" data-syndicationrights="false"><span class="js_lightbox-wrapper sc-1eow4w5-0 dUoECc"><div class="magnifier js_lightbox lightbox hide sc-1m41dwj-0 hUFSvg"><span class="iyvn34-0 iSaTEN"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" aria-label="ZoomIn icon" viewBox="0 0 18 18"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10.5 1a6.5 6.5 0 1 1-4.23 11.44l-4.42 4.41a.5.5 0 0 1-.7-.7l4.41-4.42A6.5 6.5 0 0 1 10.5 1zm0 1a5.5 5.5 0 1 0 0 11 5.5 5.5 0 0 0 0-11zm0 2c.28 0 .5.22.5.5V7h2.5a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.41v.09a.5.5 0 0 1-.5.5H11v2.5a.5.5 0 0 1-.41.5h-.09a.5.5 0 0 1-.5-.5V8H7.5a.5.5 0 0 1-.5-.41V7.5c0-.28.22-.5.5-.5H10V4.5a.5.5 0 0 1 .41-.5z"></path></svg></span></div><div style="padding-bottom:56.3%" class="image-hydration-wrapper sc-1eow4w5-3 iJyiXs"><div><img src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==" alt="Illustration for article titled The 50 most important American independent movies" data-srcset="https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fill,f_auto,fl_progressive,g_center,h_80,q_80,w_80/t8rssjviq8bojg6fwzs3.png 80w, https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fit,fl_progressive,q_80,w_320/t8rssjviq8bojg6fwzs3.png 320w, https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fit,f_auto,fl_progressive,q_80,w_470/t8rssjviq8bojg6fwzs3.png 470w, https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,fl_progressive,q_80,w_800/t8rssjviq8bojg6fwzs3.png 800w, https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,fl_progressive,q_80,w_1600/t8rssjviq8bojg6fwzs3.png 1600w" draggable="auto" data-chomp-id="t8rssjviq8bojg6fwzs3" data-format="png" data-alt="Illustration for article titled The 50 most important American independent movies" data-anim-src=""/></div></div></span><figcaption class="no-caption sc-7s1ndr-0 fbAnrV">Photo<!-- -->: <!-- -->Trailer screenshot</figcaption></div><span data-id="t8rssjviq8bojg6fwzs3" data-recommend-id="image://t8rssjviq8bojg6fwzs3" data-format="png" data-width="1352" data-height="761" data-lightbox="true" data-recommended="false" class="js_recommend"></span></figure><p class="sc-77igqf-0 hJpRRP">There’s a timeline where this record-breaking romantic comedy, about the love life of a Greek American woman with a meddlesome family, became an <span><a class="sc-145m8ut-0 jwQTmy js_link sc-1out364-0 fwjlmD" data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;External link&quot;,&quot;https://www.nytimes.com/2002/11/28/movies/big-fat-profitable-cinderella-story-greek-wedding-courts-prince-named-oscar.html&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://www.nytimes.com/2002/11/28/movies/big-fat-profitable-cinderella-story-greek-wedding-courts-prince-named-oscar.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">HBO movie of the week</a></span>. Instead, it went on to garner writer-director-star Nia Vardalos an Oscar nomination for Original Screenplay, and earn $241.4 million in North America, making it the highest-grossing rom-com of all time and spawning a cross-media franchise. Not bad statistics for a movie recently described by <span><a class="sc-145m8ut-0 jwQTmy js_link sc-1out364-0 fwjlmD" data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;Internal link&quot;,&quot;https://film.avclub.com/how-did-my-big-fat-greek-wedding-make-so-much-money-1842133129&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://film.avclub.com/how-did-my-big-fat-greek-wedding-make-so-much-money-1842133129">our resident authority on the genre</a></span> as a “small independent film with no big-name stars made for $5 million and put out in limited release in April.” [Patrick Gomez]<br/></p><hr class="gcp5ez-1 dqsVuw"/><h2 class="sc-1bwb26k-1 RjwRf" id="h220638"><a class="js_header-anchor" id=""></a><span><a class="sc-145m8ut-0 jwQTmy js_link sc-1out364-0 fwjlmD" data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;Internal link&quot;,&quot;https://film.avclub.com/lost-in-translation-1798198878&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://film.avclub.com/lost-in-translation-1798198878"><em>Lost In Translation</em></a></span> (2003)</h2><p class="sc-77igqf-0 hJpRRP"><span><a class="sc-145m8ut-0 jwQTmy js_link sc-1out364-0 fwjlmD" data-ga="[[&quot;Commerce&quot;,&quot;avfilm - The 50 most important American independent movies&quot;,&quot;&quot;]]" href="https://www.amazon.com/gp/video/detail/amzn1.dv.gti.bea9f760-bc12-dd7d-d21b-6a46ce1ffa8c?ascsubtag=25c37b1b715416666d984f14ed1c7634b1637015&amp;autoplay=1&amp;tag=kinjaavclub-20" target="_top" data-amazonasin="" data-amazontag="kinjaavclub-20" data-amazonsubtag="[t|link[p|1842597128[au|5876237249237148780[b|avclub[lt|text"><strong><em>Amazon Prime</em></strong></a></span><strong><em>, </em></strong><span><a class="sc-145m8ut-0 jwQTmy js_link sc-1out364-0 fwjlmD" data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;External link&quot;,&quot;https://play.google.com/store/movies/details?id=Tvhg97D-jvo&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://play.google.com/store/movies/details?id=Tvhg97D-jvo" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><strong><em>Google Play</em></strong></a></span><strong><em>, </em></strong><span><a class="sc-145m8ut-0 jwQTmy js_link sc-1out364-0 fwjlmD" data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;External link&quot;,&quot;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Tvhg97D-jvo&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Tvhg97D-jvo" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><strong><em>YouTube</em></strong></a></span><strong><em>, </em></strong><span><a class="sc-145m8ut-0 jwQTmy js_link sc-1out364-0 fwjlmD" data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;External link&quot;,&quot;https://www.vudu.com/content/movies/details/Lost-in-Translation/5433&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://www.vudu.com/content/movies/details/Lost-in-Translation/5433" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><strong><em>VUDU</em></strong></a></span><strong><em>, Hulu (with Starz)</em></strong></p><figure class="align--bleed js_lazy-image js_marquee-assetfigure sc-1eow4w5-1 kivedT" data-id="hqlexwhycygir8lnswpj" data-recommend-id="image://hqlexwhycygir8lnswpj" data-format="png" data-width="1369" data-height="772" data-lightbox="true" data-recommended="false" contenteditable="false" draggable="false"><div class="img-wrapper sc-1eow4w5-2 gfolHV" contenteditable="false" style="max-width:1369px" data-syndicationrights="false"><span class="js_lightbox-wrapper sc-1eow4w5-0 dUoECc"><div class="magnifier js_lightbox lightbox hide sc-1m41dwj-0 hUFSvg"><span class="iyvn34-0 iSaTEN"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" aria-label="ZoomIn icon" viewBox="0 0 18 18"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10.5 1a6.5 6.5 0 1 1-4.23 11.44l-4.42 4.41a.5.5 0 0 1-.7-.7l4.41-4.42A6.5 6.5 0 0 1 10.5 1zm0 1a5.5 5.5 0 1 0 0 11 5.5 5.5 0 0 0 0-11zm0 2c.28 0 .5.22.5.5V7h2.5a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.41v.09a.5.5 0 0 1-.5.5H11v2.5a.5.5 0 0 1-.41.5h-.09a.5.5 0 0 1-.5-.5V8H7.5a.5.5 0 0 1-.5-.41V7.5c0-.28.22-.5.5-.5H10V4.5a.5.5 0 0 1 .41-.5z"></path></svg></span></div><div style="padding-bottom:56.4%" class="image-hydration-wrapper sc-1eow4w5-3 iJyiXs"><div><img src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==" alt="Illustration for article titled The 50 most important American independent movies" data-srcset="https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fill,f_auto,fl_progressive,g_center,h_80,q_80,w_80/hqlexwhycygir8lnswpj.png 80w, https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fit,fl_progressive,q_80,w_320/hqlexwhycygir8lnswpj.png 320w, https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fit,f_auto,fl_progressive,q_80,w_470/hqlexwhycygir8lnswpj.png 470w, https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,fl_progressive,q_80,w_800/hqlexwhycygir8lnswpj.png 800w, https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,fl_progressive,q_80,w_1600/hqlexwhycygir8lnswpj.png 1600w" draggable="auto" data-chomp-id="hqlexwhycygir8lnswpj" data-format="png" data-alt="Illustration for article titled The 50 most important American independent movies" data-anim-src=""/></div></div></span><figcaption class="no-caption sc-7s1ndr-0 fbAnrV">Photo<!-- -->: <!-- -->Trailer screenshot</figcaption></div><span data-id="hqlexwhycygir8lnswpj" data-recommend-id="image://hqlexwhycygir8lnswpj" data-format="png" data-width="1369" data-height="772" data-lightbox="true" data-recommended="false" class="js_recommend"></span></figure><p class="sc-77igqf-0 hJpRRP">Sofia Coppola’s derided performance in <em>The Godfather: Part III</em> trailed her like a curse, but <em>Lost In Translation</em>—which she wrote, directed, and produced—dulled the mockery. Made for only $4 million, the comedy-drama brought in nearly $120 million, and Coppola won the Best Original Screenplay Oscar. After portraying Charlotte and Bob, unlikely friends plagued by loneliness in Tokyo, Scarlett Johansson’s and Bill Murray’s careers transformed, the former vaulting onto the A-list and the latter settling into bemused dad roles. Fan obsession over what Bob whispered into Charlotte’s ear at the end, as well as Coppola’s particular brand of sad-rich-people cinema, remains strong years later. [Roxana Hadadi]<br/></p><div class="js_movable_ad_slot bxm4mm-7 bhZEGl"><div class="bxm4mm-9 jgnxje"><label class="bxm4mm-8 kLAkkQ">Advertisement</label><div is="bulbs-dfp" class="ad-container dfp dfp-slot-MID_BANNER ad-middleboard" data-ad-unit="MID_BANNER" data-targeting="{&quot;pos&quot;:&quot;mid_banner&quot;}"></div><div class="bt-wrapper"><span data-uid="5d1b8a6cd5-384" class="bt-uid-tg" style="display:none !important;text-align:center" data-css-selector="ad-container.ad-middleboard"></span></div></div></div><hr class="gcp5ez-1 dqsVuw"/><h2 class="sc-1bwb26k-1 RjwRf" id="h220639"><a class="js_header-anchor" id=""></a><span><a class="sc-145m8ut-0 jwQTmy js_link sc-1out364-0 fwjlmD" data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;Internal link&quot;,&quot;https://film.avclub.com/the-passion-of-the-christ-1798199356&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://film.avclub.com/the-passion-of-the-christ-1798199356"><em>The Passion Of The Christ</em></a></span> (2004)</h2><p class="sc-77igqf-0 hJpRRP"><span><a class="sc-145m8ut-0 jwQTmy js_link sc-1out364-0 fwjlmD" data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;External link&quot;,&quot;https://tubitv.com/movies/475398/the_passion_of_the_christ?utm_source=google-feed&amp;tracking=google-feed&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://tubitv.com/movies/475398/the_passion_of_the_christ?utm_source=google-feed&amp;tracking=google-feed" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><strong><em>Tubi</em></strong></a></span><strong><em> (free), </em></strong><span><a class="sc-145m8ut-0 jwQTmy js_link sc-1out364-0 fwjlmD" data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;External link&quot;,&quot;https://www.vudu.com/content/movies/details/The-Passion-of-the-Christ/1077337&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://www.vudu.com/content/movies/details/The-Passion-of-the-Christ/1077337" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><strong><em>VUDU</em></strong></a></span><strong><em> (free), </em></strong><span><a class="sc-145m8ut-0 jwQTmy js_link sc-1out364-0 fwjlmD" data-ga="[[&quot;Commerce&quot;,&quot;avfilm - The 50 most important American independent movies&quot;,&quot;&quot;]]" href="https://www.amazon.com/gp/video/detail/amzn1.dv.gti.20a9f715-9272-0e0e-4b24-ce3d759cf624?ascsubtag=25c37b1b715416666d984f14ed1c7634b1637015&amp;autoplay=1&amp;tag=kinjaavclub-20" target="_top" data-amazonasin="" data-amazontag="kinjaavclub-20" data-amazonsubtag="[t|link[p|1842597128[au|5876237249237148780[b|avclub[lt|text"><strong><em>Amazon Prime</em></strong></a></span><strong><em>, </em></strong><span><a class="sc-145m8ut-0 jwQTmy js_link sc-1out364-0 fwjlmD" data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;External link&quot;,&quot;https://play.google.com/store/movies/details?id=uSP7Suodz-k&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://play.google.com/store/movies/details?id=uSP7Suodz-k" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><strong><em>Google Play</em></strong></a></span><strong><em>, </em></strong><span><a class="sc-145m8ut-0 jwQTmy js_link sc-1out364-0 fwjlmD" data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;External link&quot;,&quot;https://itunes.apple.com/us/movie/the-passion-of-the-christ/id504520946&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://itunes.apple.com/us/movie/the-passion-of-the-christ/id504520946" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><strong><em>iTunes</em></strong></a></span><strong><em>, </em></strong><span><a class="sc-145m8ut-0 jwQTmy js_link sc-1out364-0 fwjlmD" data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;External link&quot;,&quot;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uSP7Suodz-k&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uSP7Suodz-k" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><strong><em>YouTube</em></strong></a></span></p><div class="align--bleed has-video media-large video-embed embed-frame ooo3c9-0 eaUBVt"><span class="flex-video widescreen"><iframe src="/ajax/inset/iframe?id=youtube-video-uSP7Suodz-k&amp;start=0" data-chomp-id="uSP7Suodz-k" data-recommend-id="youtube://uSP7Suodz-k" id="youtube-uSP7Suodz-k" data-recommended="false" width="800" height="450" class="core-inset" frameBorder="0" scrolling="no" allowfullscreen="" webkitallowfullscreen="webkitAllowFullScreen" mozallowfullscreen="mozallowfullscreen"></iframe><span data-chomp-id="uSP7Suodz-k" data-recommend-id="youtube://uSP7Suodz-k" id="youtube-uSP7Suodz-k" data-recommended="false" class="js_recommend"></span></span></div><p class="sc-77igqf-0 hJpRRP">Before Mel Gibson’s self-financed blockbuster for believers, Christian studios dealt primarily in low-budget fare. <em>The</em> <em>Passion Of The Christ</em> changed everything, first by folding an A-lister and some awards-worthy craft into the faith-based genre, then by demonstrating just how little such films actually needed a secular audience—Gibson spent months courting evangelical leaders, who drummed up much of the movie’s record-breaking $600 million from their congregations. <span><a class="sc-145m8ut-0 jwQTmy js_link sc-1out364-0 fwjlmD" data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;Internal link&quot;,&quot;https://www.avclub.com/the-passion-of-the-christ-was-the-blunt-force-weapon-ev-1832999651&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://www.avclub.com/the-passion-of-the-christ-was-the-blunt-force-weapon-ev-1832999651">Leaning hard</a></span> into the subsequent controversies—the gratuitous violence, the anti-Semitism—Gibson also made divisiveness a key appeal for defensive Christians, who turned out in droves to make <em>Passion</em> the highest-grossing independent film of all time. The impact resounds: Today’s evangelical filmmakers are often just as interested in flaming the culture wars as they are in saving souls. [Randall Colburn]<br/></p><hr class="gcp5ez-1 dqsVuw"/><h2 class="sc-1bwb26k-1 RjwRf" id="h220640"><a class="js_header-anchor" id=""></a><span><a class="sc-145m8ut-0 jwQTmy js_link sc-1out364-0 fwjlmD" data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;Internal link&quot;,&quot;https://film.avclub.com/garden-state-1798199818&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://film.avclub.com/garden-state-1798199818"><strong><em>Garden State</em></strong></a></span><strong><em> </em>(2004)</strong></h2><p class="sc-77igqf-0 hJpRRP"> <span><a class="sc-145m8ut-0 jwQTmy js_link sc-1out364-0 fwjlmD" data-ga="[[&quot;Commerce&quot;,&quot;avfilm - The 50 most important American independent movies&quot;,&quot;&quot;]]" href="https://www.amazon.com/gp/video/detail/amzn1.dv.gti.c8a9f70c-f4b5-1daf-4441-41d9989455e3?ascsubtag=25c37b1b715416666d984f14ed1c7634b1637015&amp;autoplay=1&amp;tag=kinjaavclub-20" target="_top" data-amazonasin="" data-amazontag="kinjaavclub-20" data-amazonsubtag="[t|link[p|1842597128[au|5876237249237148780[b|avclub[lt|text"><strong><em>Amazon Prime</em></strong></a></span><strong><em>, </em></strong><span><a class="sc-145m8ut-0 jwQTmy js_link sc-1out364-0 fwjlmD" data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;External link&quot;,&quot;https://play.google.com/store/movies/details?id=1EYYGsfruM4&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://play.google.com/store/movies/details?id=1EYYGsfruM4" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><strong><em>Google Play</em></strong></a></span><strong><em>, </em></strong><span><a class="sc-145m8ut-0 jwQTmy js_link sc-1out364-0 fwjlmD" data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;External link&quot;,&quot;https://itunes.apple.com/us/movie/garden-state/id270109340&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://itunes.apple.com/us/movie/garden-state/id270109340" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><strong><em>iTunes</em></strong></a></span><strong><em>, </em></strong><span><a class="sc-145m8ut-0 jwQTmy js_link sc-1out364-0 fwjlmD" data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;External link&quot;,&quot;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1EYYGsfruM4&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1EYYGsfruM4" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><strong><em>YouTube</em></strong></a></span><strong><em>, </em></strong><span><a class="sc-145m8ut-0 jwQTmy js_link sc-1out364-0 fwjlmD" data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;External link&quot;,&quot;https://www.vudu.com/content/movies/details/Garden-State/8418&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://www.vudu.com/content/movies/details/Garden-State/8418" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><strong><em>VUDU</em></strong></a></span><strong><em>, </em></strong><span><a class="sc-145m8ut-0 jwQTmy js_link sc-1out364-0 fwjlmD" data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;External link&quot;,&quot;https://play.maxgo.com/page/urn:hbo:page:home&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://play.maxgo.com/page/urn:hbo:page:home" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><strong><em>Cinemax</em></strong></a></span></p><div class="align--bleed has-video media-large video-embed embed-frame ooo3c9-0 eaUBVt"><span class="flex-video widescreen"><iframe src="/ajax/inset/iframe?id=youtube-video-Ziwr4f5eR0M&amp;start=0" data-chomp-id="Ziwr4f5eR0M" data-recommend-id="youtube://Ziwr4f5eR0M" id="youtube-Ziwr4f5eR0M" data-recommended="false" width="800" height="450" class="core-inset" frameBorder="0" scrolling="no" allowfullscreen="" webkitallowfullscreen="webkitAllowFullScreen" mozallowfullscreen="mozallowfullscreen"></iframe><span data-chomp-id="Ziwr4f5eR0M" data-recommend-id="youtube://Ziwr4f5eR0M" id="youtube-Ziwr4f5eR0M" data-recommended="false" class="js_recommend"></span></span></div><p class="sc-77igqf-0 hJpRRP">It’s telling that when Zach Braff won a major award for his somber-sweet directorial debut, it was not an Oscar but a Grammy, for Best Soundtrack Album. <em>Garden State</em>’s carefully curated mixtape of Shins songs, old Simon and Garfunkel tunes, and indie hits lifted directly off of Braff’s iPod may not have changed your life, as Natalie Portman’s Sam promises, but it did set the sound of indie films for the<!-- --> decade to come. The movie itself—a meditation on one young white dude’s dead-eyed ennui—had its share of imitators, too. But it was its accompanying set of tracks that touched a chord with people, turning musical moping into a precision filmmaking art. [William Hughes]<br/></p><div class="js_movable_ad_slot bxm4mm-7 bhZEGl"><div class="bxm4mm-9 jgnxje"><label class="bxm4mm-8 kLAkkQ">Advertisement</label><div is="bulbs-dfp" class="ad-container dfp dfp-slot-MID_BANNER ad-middleboard" data-ad-unit="MID_BANNER" data-targeting="{&quot;pos&quot;:&quot;mid_banner&quot;}"></div><div class="bt-wrapper"><span data-uid="5d1b8a6cd5-384" class="bt-uid-tg" style="display:none !important;text-align:center" data-css-selector="ad-container.ad-middleboard"></span></div></div></div><hr class="gcp5ez-1 dqsVuw"/><h2 class="sc-1bwb26k-1 RjwRf" id="h220641"><a class="js_header-anchor" id=""></a><span><a class="sc-145m8ut-0 jwQTmy js_link sc-1out364-0 fwjlmD" data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;Internal link&quot;,&quot;https://film.avclub.com/the-new-cult-canon-primer-1798213694&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://film.avclub.com/the-new-cult-canon-primer-1798213694"><strong><em>Primer</em></strong></a></span><strong><em> </em>(2004)</strong></h2><p class="sc-77igqf-0 hJpRRP"><span><a class="sc-145m8ut-0 jwQTmy js_link sc-1out364-0 fwjlmD" data-ga="[[&quot;Commerce&quot;,&quot;avfilm - The 50 most important American independent movies&quot;,&quot;&quot;]]" href="https://www.amazon.com/gp/video/detail/amzn1.dv.gti.2ca9f74e-4f59-3c7c-a904-20ca5d82cd78?ascsubtag=25c37b1b715416666d984f14ed1c7634b1637015&amp;autoplay=1&amp;tag=kinjaavclub-20" target="_top" data-amazonasin="" data-amazontag="kinjaavclub-20" data-amazonsubtag="[t|link[p|1842597128[au|5876237249237148780[b|avclub[lt|text"><strong><em>Amazon Prime</em></strong></a></span><strong><em>, </em></strong><span><a class="sc-145m8ut-0 jwQTmy js_link sc-1out364-0 fwjlmD" data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;External link&quot;,&quot;https://play.google.com/store/movies/details?id=9A7fCKM4ERA&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://play.google.com/store/movies/details?id=9A7fCKM4ERA" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><strong><em>Google Play</em></strong></a></span><strong><em>, </em></strong><span><a class="sc-145m8ut-0 jwQTmy js_link sc-1out364-0 fwjlmD" data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;External link&quot;,&quot;https://itunes.apple.com/us/movie/primer/id536457427&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://itunes.apple.com/us/movie/primer/id536457427" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><strong><em>iTunes</em></strong></a></span><strong><em>, </em></strong><span><a class="sc-145m8ut-0 jwQTmy js_link sc-1out364-0 fwjlmD" data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;External link&quot;,&quot;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9A7fCKM4ERA&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9A7fCKM4ERA" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><strong><em>YouTube</em></strong></a></span></p><figure class="align--bleed js_lazy-image js_marquee-assetfigure sc-1eow4w5-1 kivedT" data-id="yy2q2zbuqnhjib9cewxq" data-recommend-id="image://yy2q2zbuqnhjib9cewxq" data-format="png" data-width="1402" data-height="785" data-lightbox="true" data-recommended="false" contenteditable="false" draggable="false"><div class="img-wrapper sc-1eow4w5-2 gfolHV" contenteditable="false" style="max-width:1402px" data-syndicationrights="false"><span class="js_lightbox-wrapper sc-1eow4w5-0 dUoECc"><div class="magnifier js_lightbox lightbox hide sc-1m41dwj-0 hUFSvg"><span class="iyvn34-0 iSaTEN"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" aria-label="ZoomIn icon" viewBox="0 0 18 18"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10.5 1a6.5 6.5 0 1 1-4.23 11.44l-4.42 4.41a.5.5 0 0 1-.7-.7l4.41-4.42A6.5 6.5 0 0 1 10.5 1zm0 1a5.5 5.5 0 1 0 0 11 5.5 5.5 0 0 0 0-11zm0 2c.28 0 .5.22.5.5V7h2.5a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.41v.09a.5.5 0 0 1-.5.5H11v2.5a.5.5 0 0 1-.41.5h-.09a.5.5 0 0 1-.5-.5V8H7.5a.5.5 0 0 1-.5-.41V7.5c0-.28.22-.5.5-.5H10V4.5a.5.5 0 0 1 .41-.5z"></path></svg></span></div><div style="padding-bottom:56%" class="image-hydration-wrapper sc-1eow4w5-3 iJyiXs"><div><img src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==" alt="Illustration for article titled The 50 most important American independent movies" data-srcset="https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fill,f_auto,fl_progressive,g_center,h_80,q_80,w_80/yy2q2zbuqnhjib9cewxq.png 80w, https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fit,fl_progressive,q_80,w_320/yy2q2zbuqnhjib9cewxq.png 320w, https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fit,f_auto,fl_progressive,q_80,w_470/yy2q2zbuqnhjib9cewxq.png 470w, https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,fl_progressive,q_80,w_800/yy2q2zbuqnhjib9cewxq.png 800w, https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,fl_progressive,q_80,w_1600/yy2q2zbuqnhjib9cewxq.png 1600w" draggable="auto" data-chomp-id="yy2q2zbuqnhjib9cewxq" data-format="png" data-alt="Illustration for article titled The 50 most important American independent movies" data-anim-src=""/></div></div></span><figcaption class="no-caption sc-7s1ndr-0 fbAnrV">Photo<!-- -->: <!-- -->Trailer screenshot</figcaption></div><span data-id="yy2q2zbuqnhjib9cewxq" data-recommend-id="image://yy2q2zbuqnhjib9cewxq" data-format="png" data-width="1402" data-height="785" data-lightbox="true" data-recommended="false" class="js_recommend"></span></figure><p class="sc-77igqf-0 hJpRRP">In a better world, <em>Primer </em>would have launched Shane Carruth, its writer/director/producer/editor/head musician/star, into the indie-filmmaking stratosphere, if for no more than the sheer amount of science fiction mileage he managed to eke out of a minuscule $7,000 budget and a “time machine” prop so simple a child could build it in a lazy afternoon. Instead, Carruth has completed only one other film (the equally intriguing, if more expensive, <span><a class="sc-145m8ut-0 jwQTmy js_link sc-1out364-0 fwjlmD" data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;Internal link&quot;,&quot;https://film.avclub.com/upstream-color-1798176362&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://film.avclub.com/upstream-color-1798176362"><em>Upstream Color</em></a></span>), and <em>Primer </em>remains a fascinating puzzle box, as intriguing for its singular expression of one man’s interests—technical jargon, unforeseen consequences, and the easily corruptible nature of extremely boring men—as for its infamously complex and obscure time-travel plot. [William Hughes]<br/></p><hr class="gcp5ez-1 dqsVuw"/><h2 class="sc-1bwb26k-1 RjwRf" id="h220642"><a class="js_header-anchor" id=""></a><span><a class="sc-145m8ut-0 jwQTmy js_link sc-1out364-0 fwjlmD" data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;Internal link&quot;,&quot;https://film.avclub.com/little-miss-sunshine-1798201889&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://film.avclub.com/little-miss-sunshine-1798201889"><em>Little Miss Sunshine</em></a></span> (2006)</h2><p class="sc-77igqf-0 hJpRRP"><span><a class="sc-145m8ut-0 jwQTmy js_link sc-1out364-0 fwjlmD" data-ga="[[&quot;Commerce&quot;,&quot;avfilm - The 50 most important American independent movies&quot;,&quot;&quot;]]" href="https://www.amazon.com/gp/video/detail/amzn1.dv.gti.1aa9f79e-33ca-749b-3900-85ddd86964de?ascsubtag=25c37b1b715416666d984f14ed1c7634b1637015&amp;autoplay=1&amp;tag=kinjaavclub-20" target="_top" data-amazonasin="" data-amazontag="kinjaavclub-20" data-amazonsubtag="[t|link[p|1842597128[au|5876237249237148780[b|avclub[lt|text"><strong><em>Amazon Prime</em></strong></a></span><strong><em>, </em></strong><span><a class="sc-145m8ut-0 jwQTmy js_link sc-1out364-0 fwjlmD" data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;External link&quot;,&quot;https://play.google.com/store/movies/details?id=yMVrxs-d5Xk&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://play.google.com/store/movies/details?id=yMVrxs-d5Xk" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><strong><em>Google Play</em></strong></a></span><strong><em>, </em></strong><span><a class="sc-145m8ut-0 jwQTmy js_link sc-1out364-0 fwjlmD" data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;External link&quot;,&quot;https://itunes.apple.com/us/movie/little-miss-sunshine/id287984473&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://itunes.apple.com/us/movie/little-miss-sunshine/id287984473" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><strong><em>iTunes</em></strong></a></span><strong><em>, </em></strong><span><a class="sc-145m8ut-0 jwQTmy js_link sc-1out364-0 fwjlmD" data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;External link&quot;,&quot;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yMVrxs-d5Xk&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yMVrxs-d5Xk" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><strong><em>YouTube</em></strong></a></span><strong><em>, </em></strong><span><a class="sc-145m8ut-0 jwQTmy js_link sc-1out364-0 fwjlmD" data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;External link&quot;,&quot;https://www.vudu.com/content/movies/details/Little-Miss-Sunshine/8982&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://www.vudu.com/co