EKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==" alt="Illustration for article titled The 50 most important American independent movies" data-srcset="https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fill,f_auto,fl_progressive,g_center,h_80,q_80,w_80/obcfr6ycd97rlnmpwz4k.png 80w, https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fit,fl_progressive,q_80,w_320/obcfr6ycd97rlnmpwz4k.png 320w, https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fit,f_auto,fl_progressive,q_80,w_470/obcfr6ycd97rlnmpwz4k.png 470w, https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,fl_progressive,q_80,w_800/obcfr6ycd97rlnmpwz4k.png 800w, https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,fl_progressive,q_80,w_1600/obcfr6ycd97rlnmpwz4k.png 1600w" draggable="auto" data-chomp-id="obcfr6ycd97rlnmpwz4k" data-format="png" data-alt="Illustration for article titled The 50 most important American independent movies" data-anim-src=""/></div></div></span><figcaption class="no-caption sc-7s1ndr-0 fbAnrV">Photo<!-- -->: <!-- -->Trailer screenshot</figcaption></div><span data-id="obcfr6ycd97rlnmpwz4k" data-recommend-id="image://obcfr6ycd97rlnmpwz4k" data-format="png" data-width="1377" data-height="775" data-lightbox="true" data-recommended="false" class="js_recommend"></span></figure><p class="sc-77igqf-0 hJpRRP">Already a mainstay of the American indie scene from the mid- to late-2000s, Greta Gerwig first brought her signature charm to the Noah Baumbach universe in 2010’s <span><a class="sc-145m8ut-0 jwQTmy js_link sc-1out364-0 fwjlmD" data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;Internal link&quot;,&quot;https://film.avclub.com/greenberg-1798164557&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://film.avclub.com/greenberg-1798164557"><em>Greenberg</em></a></span>. But it was <em>Frances Ha</em>, which she co-wrote and starred<!-- --> in,<!-- --> two years later, that turned their collaboration into a full-fledged partnership. While harking back to the spirit of the French New Wave, the bittersweet black-and-white comedy also looks forward, reinforcing Gerwig’s status as a major creative force in her own right, and anticipating the directorial successes that she would soon achieve with <span><a class="sc-145m8ut-0 jwQTmy js_link sc-1out364-0 fwjlmD" data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;Internal link&quot;,&quot;https://www.avclub.com/greta-gerwigs-uproarious-beautiful-lady-bird-puts-the-1819996029&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://www.avclub.com/greta-gerwigs-uproarious-beautiful-lady-bird-puts-the-1819996029"><em>Lady Bird</em></a></span><em> </em>and <span><a class="sc-145m8ut-0 jwQTmy js_link sc-1out364-0 fwjlmD" data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;Internal link&quot;,&quot;https://film.avclub.com/greta-gerwig-s-little-women-vibrantly-celebrates-ambiti-1840009176&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://film.avclub.com/greta-gerwig-s-little-women-vibrantly-celebrates-ambiti-1840009176"><em>Little Women</em></a></span>. [Lawrence Garcia]<br/></p><div class="js_movable_ad_slot bxm4mm-7 bhZEGl"><div class="bxm4mm-9 jgnxje"><label class="bxm4mm-8 kLAkkQ">Advertisement</label><div is="bulbs-dfp" class="ad-container dfp dfp-slot-MID_BANNER ad-middleboard" data-ad-unit="MID_BANNER" data-targeting="{&quot;pos&quot;:&quot;mid_banner&quot;}"></div><div class="bt-wrapper"><span data-uid="5d1b8a6cd5-384" class="bt-uid-tg" style="display:none !important;text-align:center" data-css-selector="ad-container.ad-middleboard"></span></div></div></div><hr class="gcp5ez-1 dqsVuw"/><h2 class="sc-1bwb26k-1 RjwRf" id="h220645"><a class="js_header-anchor" id=""></a><span><a class="sc-145m8ut-0 jwQTmy js_link sc-1out364-0 fwjlmD" data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;Internal link&quot;,&quot;https://film.avclub.com/one-of-2016-s-best-moonlight-unfolds-a-coming-of-age-s-1798189203&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://film.avclub.com/one-of-2016-s-best-moonlight-unfolds-a-coming-of-age-s-1798189203"><em>Moonlight</em></a></span> (2016)</h2><p class="sc-77igqf-0 hJpRRP"><span><a class="sc-145m8ut-0 jwQTmy js_link sc-1out364-0 fwjlmD" data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;External link&quot;,&quot;https://www.netflix.com/watch/80121348?source=35&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://www.netflix.com/watch/80121348?source=35" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><strong><em>Netflix</em></strong></a></span><strong><em>, </em></strong><span><a class="sc-145m8ut-0 jwQTmy js_link sc-1out364-0 fwjlmD" data-ga="[[&quot;Commerce&quot;,&quot;avfilm - The 50 most important American independent movies&quot;,&quot;&quot;]]" href="https://www.amazon.com/gp/video/detail/amzn1.dv.gti.56acc492-150c-d5b2-9301-b028147a4f27?ascsubtag=25c37b1b715416666d984f14ed1c7634b1637015&amp;autoplay=1&amp;tag=kinjaavclub-20" target="_top" data-amazonasin="" data-amazontag="kinjaavclub-20" data-amazonsubtag="[t|link[p|1842597128[au|5876237249237148780[b|avclub[lt|text"><strong><em>Amazon Prime</em></strong></a></span><strong><em>, </em></strong><span><a class="sc-145m8ut-0 jwQTmy js_link sc-1out364-0 fwjlmD" data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;External link&quot;,&quot;https://play.google.com/store/movies/details?id=q1CRTX8Kdag&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://play.google.com/store/movies/details?id=q1CRTX8Kdag" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><strong><em>Google Play</em></strong></a></span><strong><em>, </em></strong><span><a class="sc-145m8ut-0 jwQTmy js_link sc-1out364-0 fwjlmD" data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;External link&quot;,&quot;https://itunes.apple.com/us/movie/moonlight/id1163932416&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://itunes.apple.com/us/movie/moonlight/id1163932416" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><strong><em>iTunes</em></strong></a></span><strong><em>, </em></strong><span><a class="sc-145m8ut-0 jwQTmy js_link sc-1out364-0 fwjlmD" data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;External link&quot;,&quot;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=q1CRTX8Kdag&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=q1CRTX8Kdag" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><strong><em>YouTube</em></strong></a></span><strong><em>, </em></strong><span><a class="sc-145m8ut-0 jwQTmy js_link sc-1out364-0 fwjlmD" data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;External link&quot;,&quot;https://www.vudu.com/content/movies/details/Moonlight/835625&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://www.vudu.com/content/movies/details/Moonlight/835625" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><strong><em>VUDU</em></strong></a></span></p><figure class="align--bleed js_lazy-image js_marquee-assetfigure sc-1eow4w5-1 kivedT" data-id="mxy1gdagodlmoxc4d5vw" data-recommend-id="image://mxy1gdagodlmoxc4d5vw" data-format="png" data-width="1033" data-height="583" data-lightbox="true" data-recommended="false" contenteditable="false" draggable="false"><div class="img-wrapper sc-1eow4w5-2 gfolHV" contenteditable="false" style="max-width:1033px" data-syndicationrights="false"><span class="js_lightbox-wrapper sc-1eow4w5-0 dUoECc"><div class="magnifier js_lightbox lightbox hide sc-1m41dwj-0 hUFSvg"><span class="iyvn34-0 iSaTEN"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" aria-label="ZoomIn icon" viewBox="0 0 18 18"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10.5 1a6.5 6.5 0 1 1-4.23 11.44l-4.42 4.41a.5.5 0 0 1-.7-.7l4.41-4.42A6.5 6.5 0 0 1 10.5 1zm0 1a5.5 5.5 0 1 0 0 11 5.5 5.5 0 0 0 0-11zm0 2c.28 0 .5.22.5.5V7h2.5a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.41v.09a.5.5 0 0 1-.5.5H11v2.5a.5.5 0 0 1-.41.5h-.09a.5.5 0 0 1-.5-.5V8H7.5a.5.5 0 0 1-.5-.41V7.5c0-.28.22-.5.5-.5H10V4.5a.5.5 0 0 1 .41-.5z"></path></svg></span></div><div style="padding-bottom:56.4%" class="image-hydration-wrapper sc-1eow4w5-3 iJyiXs"><div><img src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==" alt="Illustration for article titled The 50 most important American independent movies" data-srcset="https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fill,f_auto,fl_progressive,g_center,h_80,q_80,w_80/mxy1gdagodlmoxc4d5vw.png 80w, https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fit,fl_progressive,q_80,w_320/mxy1gdagodlmoxc4d5vw.png 320w, https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fit,f_auto,fl_progressive,q_80,w_470/mxy1gdagodlmoxc4d5vw.png 470w, https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,fl_progressive,q_80,w_800/mxy1gdagodlmoxc4d5vw.png 800w" draggable="auto" data-chomp-id="mxy1gdagodlmoxc4d5vw" data-format="png" data-alt="Illustration for article titled The 50 most important American independent movies" data-anim-src=""/></div></div></span><figcaption class="no-caption sc-7s1ndr-0 fbAnrV">Photo<!-- -->: <!-- -->Trailer screenshot</figcaption></div><span data-id="mxy1gdagodlmoxc4d5vw" data-recommend-id="image://mxy1gdagodlmoxc4d5vw" data-format="png" data-width="1033" data-height="583" data-lightbox="true" data-recommended="false" class="js_recommend"></span></figure><p class="sc-77igqf-0 hJpRRP"><em>Moonlight</em>’s big victory at the Academy Awards will probably forever be associated with the <span><a class="sc-145m8ut-0 jwQTmy js_link sc-1out364-0 fwjlmD" data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;Internal link&quot;,&quot;https://news.avclub.com/what-the-hell-just-happened-1798258513&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://news.avclub.com/what-the-hell-just-happened-1798258513">snafu surrounding it</a></span>. But it would have been plenty shocking to hear Warren Beatty just read the <em>right</em> title. After all, Barry Jenkins’ lyrical coming-of-age drama, told across three distinct chapters of a young man’s life, boasts the lowest budget of any Best Picture winner in history. What’s more, it’s the kind of movie—intimate, poetic, concerned with the lives of Black, queer, and impoverished Americans—that the Oscars have traditionally snubbed. Three years later, there are brilliant-blue glimmers of Jenkins’ triumph in plenty of new indie visions, including a few handled by A24, whose reputation as the boutique arthouse distributor of the moment solidified with <em>Moonlight</em>. [A.<!-- -->A. Dowd]<br/></p><hr class="gcp5ez-1 dqsVuw"/><h2 class="sc-1bwb26k-1 RjwRf" id="h220646"><a class="js_header-anchor" id=""></a><span><a class="sc-145m8ut-0 jwQTmy js_link sc-1out364-0 fwjlmD" data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;Internal link&quot;,&quot;https://film.avclub.com/jordan-peele-shifts-from-comedy-to-horror-with-the-smar-1798190618&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://film.avclub.com/jordan-peele-shifts-from-comedy-to-horror-with-the-smar-1798190618"><strong><em>Get Out</em></strong></a></span><strong> (2017)</strong></h2><p class="sc-77igqf-0 hJpRRP"> <span><a class="sc-145m8ut-0 jwQTmy js_link sc-1out364-0 fwjlmD" data-ga="[[&quot;Commerce&quot;,&quot;avfilm - The 50 most important American independent movies&quot;,&quot;&quot;]]" href="https://www.amazon.com/gp/video/detail/amzn1.dv.gti.34ad9d89-2a6b-11a1-c5c3-27569d5ee969?ascsubtag=25c37b1b715416666d984f14ed1c7634b1637015&amp;autoplay=1&amp;tag=kinjaavclub-20" target="_top" data-amazonasin="" data-amazontag="kinjaavclub-20" data-amazonsubtag="[t|link[p|1842597128[au|5876237249237148780[b|avclub[lt|text"><strong><em>Amazon Prime</em></strong></a></span><strong><em>, </em></strong><span><a class="sc-145m8ut-0 jwQTmy js_link sc-1out364-0 fwjlmD" data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;External link&quot;,&quot;https://play.google.com/store/movies/details?id=YfLSryEaAfw&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://play.google.com/store/movies/details?id=YfLSryEaAfw" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><strong><em>Google Play</em></strong></a></span><strong><em>, </em></strong><span><a class="sc-145m8ut-0 jwQTmy js_link sc-1out364-0 fwjlmD" data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;External link&quot;,&quot;https://itunes.apple.com/us/movie/get-out/id1202441786&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://itunes.apple.com/us/movie/get-out/id1202441786" target="_bla